        <p class="section-intro">
          The package is ATF's own count, in ATF's own words. Repeal is the
          loudest group. Clarify is the largest, and most of its substance flies
          under the radar — including a new statutory definition of "willfully"
          that will reshape how license revocations work.
        </p>

